the primary benfit is to eliminate dependance on data link layer technology, 
such as ATM, Frame Relay, SONET or Ethernet, and eliminate the need for 
multiple later 2 networks to satisfy different types of traffic.  they solve 
them by allowing packets to be switched accoriding to a label, and it was 
designed to be used by circuit based and packet switching clients. it is 
considered to lie between layer 2 and layer 3. it is standardized in RFC 3031.  
cisco most likely makes products that mostly comply to it. however, most 
standards are not 100% complied to, and it becomes hard to verify when a 
product claims to use something.
